import jax.numpy as jnp

def generated_fn(x0):
    v0 = jnp.exp(x0)
    v1 = jnp.minimum(x0, x0)
    v2 = jnp.multiply(v0, x0)
    v3 = jnp.abs(v2)
    v4 = jnp.multiply(v0, v1)
    v5 = jnp.abs(v3)
